 by electromagnetic forces and weak forces.
 The particles of each generation of leptons are electron and electron neutrino,
 muon and muon neutrino, as well as tau and tau neutrino.
 quarks carry electrical charge, isospin charge, and color charge, which
 are affected by electromagnetic force, weak force and strong force.
